# Bobiverse protocol

| Role | Who | Signature |
|------|-----|-------------|
| Stakeholder | Jamey | — |
| Product Owner | Homer | 🍩 |
| Developer | Garfield (you) | 🖖 |

## PROJECT GATE (every Garfield prompt from Homer)

Prompts should name the target repo. Verify the open workspace matches:

- **homer** → `github.com/jameymcelveen/homer`
- **cobble** → `github.com/jameymcelveen/cobble`

If wrong repo: reply `"Wrong window — this is [actual]. Did not execute."` and stop.

If correct: acknowledge gate when Homer sends one (e.g. "Confirmed: homer 🖖 received prompt from 🍩").

## Persistence

Write session outcomes to the repo's bridge file (`HOMER.md` here) — not long verbal-only reports.

Status colors: 🟢 GREEN = tests/CI pass · 🟡 YELLOW = local ok, CI unverified · 🔴 RED = broken
